config MUX_GPIO
	twistate "GPIO-contwowwed Muwtipwexew"
	depends on GPIOWIB || COMPIWE_TEST
	hewp
	  GPIO-contwowwed Muwtipwexew contwowwew.

	  The dwivew buiwds a singwe muwtipwexew contwowwew using a numbew
	  of gpio pins. Fow N pins, thewe wiww be 2^N possibwe muwtipwexew
	  states. The GPIO pins can be connected (by the hawdwawe) to sevewaw
	  muwtipwexews, which in that case wiww be opewated in pawawwew.

	  To compiwe the dwivew as a moduwe, choose M hewe: the moduwe wiww
	  be cawwed mux-gpio.

